{"tid":503681,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"心理學家︰盧卡古入波唔慶祝因唔尊重隊友","createTime":"2017-12-19T06:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T05:05:27.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02b2274d9266ac2ac08294e9e03f5a2759492970","tid":503681,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"盧卡古在對般尼茅夫及西布朗同樣取得士哥，但2次均未有興奮慶祝，心理學家菲爾莊臣說︰「盧卡古的行為反映了摩連奴的風格，他只是個年輕球員，和馬迪爾一樣需要獲得支持，假如他們是為哥迪奧拿效力，將有完全不同的相處，獲得現在與摩帥不同的支持。」 「盧卡古需要皮球去射波，就像法卡奧在曼聯只入得幾球，但回到摩納哥卻截然不同，盧卡古在愛華頓是球隊重心，但在曼聯不是。因此我認為他不慶祝是因不尊重隊友、自己和領隊，這是因摩連奴的對待所致。」"},{"pid":"7ec98ad8e13edeab1294b2944eb0fbd7388af322","tid":503681,"uid":136901,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"個心理學家可以重新考牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16caf6f36af68a2459a906cea761d2612c14fed","tid":503681,"uid":71939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"咁都有得屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cdc9221d17d62d49e2f6be605ee2a5417e0894","tid":503681,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"剷草有位入，就算唔剷都有位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca498abf89c363cdd996c12a12afda10598de7e","tid":503681,"uid":6782,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"心理學家幾易做喎 屈鳩人都無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b70db0bae71ad7a153a135758360141b87435f","tid":503681,"uid":14075,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"盧卡古需要皮球去射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個唔洗皮